snippet.title: REMOVE AMBER HEARD FROM DCEU- PETITION  STARTED- #METOO BACKFIRES
snippet.description:
Either it's Johnny Depp, Chris Hardwick or Amber Heard, #METOO, SJWism and feminism is destroying Entertainment industry. Let the law do its job and Heard will pay for her mistakes. STOP BOYCOTTS and mob lynching.
It all seems very nice until we see that it's the same victim culture that Heard used. Victim culture needs to be destroyed. If you're paid in millions, you're not a victim of oppression.
Main article- https://boundingintocomics.com/2019/03/21/petition-created-to-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2-after-johnny-depps-lawsuit/
